      "id": "PopularPost152144",
      "post_content": "Unless you're playing a slow deck and need to sideboard in some help against fast aggro. In that case, [Holy Day](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Holy Day) is a winner. Jacerator decks were a pain to play against for a reason, even though it wasn't too difficult to disrupt their artifacts and enchantments. ",
