    {
      "id": "PopularPost263566",
      "post_content": "It was a neat combat trick in limited, at the time, I'm sure. As it stands, the lack of preventing damage to players (or planeswalkers) seal its fate. It's bad. See [Fog](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fog) and [Holy Day](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Holy Day) for examples of how to do this better, for cheaper. And see [Safe Passage](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Safe Passage)'s rating for how valuable the added protection is considered to be. It costs more, and it's still better.",
      "posted_by": "Reversed",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost263566\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">It was a neat combat trick in limited, at the time, I'm sure. As it stands, the lack of preventing damage to players (or planeswalkers) seal its fate. It's bad. See <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fog\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fog\">Fog</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Holy Day\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Holy Day\">Holy Day</a> for examples of how to do this better, for cheaper. And see <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Safe Passage\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Safe Passage\">Safe Passage</a>'s rating for how valuable the added protection is considered to be. It costs more, and it's still better.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '263566'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy79603\">Reversed</span>\r\n                                (8/21/2012 8:21:14 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepea