      "id": "PopularPost280528",
      "post_content": "Judging by the comments here, it seems no one noticed that [Holy Day](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Holy Day) prevents \\_combat\\_ damage, not all damage, making the two cards hard to actually compare, since they don't aim at the same thing.",
      "posted_by": "Belz_",
